WEBVTT

00:00.348 --> 00:02.354
他们为大家表演一个小品
They will perform a comedy sketch for everyone

00:02.805 --> 00:03.656
名字叫
It's called

00:04.145 --> 00:04.495
（主持人名）
(Host Name)

00:04.616 --> 00:05.440
别报别报
Don't announce it!

00:06.528 --> 00:07.344
什么
What?

00:07.460 --> 00:08.260
演员还没到呢
The actor hasn't arrived yet

00:08.696 --> 00:09.676
这怎么办呢
What should we do now?

00:09.700 --> 00:10.180
这闹的
What a mess

00:13.097 --> 00:13.897
是不是能给个顺序
Could we rearrange the order a bit

00:14.320 --> 00:15.540
上下给颠倒一下
Maybe switch the sequence around

00:16.167 --> 00:17.175
那节目都乱了
Then the whole program would be thrown into chaos

00:18.280 --> 00:19.080
咱们是电影演员之间
We're all film actors here

00:19.220 --> 00:20.180
互相去通融一下
Let's help each other out a little

00:22.240 --> 00:23.040
你这怎么电影演员
What kind of film actor are you

00:23.260 --> 00:24.440
怎么要就要走后门
Why are you trying to use the back door

00:26.188 --> 00:27.021
演员到底应该没有到
So the actor really hasn't arrived

00:27.089 --> 00:27.754
我听见了
I heard that

00:27.976 --> 00:28.736
演员没有到
The actor hasn't arrived

00:28.760 --> 00:29.279
演员没到
The actor isn't here

00:29.934 --> 00:30.796
演员没到找一找
The actor isn't here? Go look for him

00:30.820 --> 00:31.980
我先回去麻烦您可以找一下
I'll head back first. Please try to find him

00:32.080 --> 00:33.260
我去找找找
I'll go look for him

00:33.425 --> 00:33.845
在什么地方
Where is he

00:33.940 --> 00:35.375
不远就在八达岭
Not far. He's at Badaling." (Note: Badaling is where the Great Wall is located, ages away from the Spring Festival Gala studio.)

00:35.400 --> 00:36.900
八达岭我上哪找去
Badaling? How am I supposed to find him there?

00:38.374 --> 00:38.955
我说啊
Listen...

00:38.980 --> 00:40.060
这有一个呢
Here's someone

00:40.400 --> 00:40.710
师傅
Sir

00:41.100 --> 00:42.000
师傅
Sir

00:42.975 --> 00:44.224
咱们这怎么着
What's going on here

00:44.260 --> 00:45.340
缺演员是怎么着
Do you need an actor?

00:45.560 --> 00:46.160
缺演员
We are short of actors

00:46.400 --> 00:47.420
三位师傅
Sir

00:47.540 --> 00:48.340
你们看我怎么样
what do you think of me

00:50.060 --> 00:51.243
我自己觉着还 还不错
To be honest, I think I'm not bad

00:52.260 --> 00:53.220
行了你
Oh, Come on

00:54.548 --> 00:54.960
你干什么的
What do you do for a living

00:55.100 --> 00:55.933
你要干什么
What are you up to

00:56.623 --> 00:57.943
拍电影嘛
Making movies, right

00:58.297 --> 00:59.257
不就是吃吃喝喝玩玩乐
Isn't it just eating, drinking, and having fun

00:59.907 --> 01:00.856
游山玩水
traveling and sightseeing

01:01.332 --> 01:01.773
哎 同志同志
Hey, comrade, comrade

01:02.403 --> 01:03.460
你想拍电影吗
Do you want to be in a movie

01:04.059 --> 01:04.960
想啊 我都不认
Of course I do

01:04.960 --> 01:06.040
你想拍电影 你别那么说
Don't put it that way

01:06.159 --> 01:07.960
拍电影那是一件工作呢
Making films is a job

01:08.403 --> 01:09.566
是 艰苦的革命工作
A tough revolutionary job

01:10.234 --> 01:10.886
你不想拍吗
You don't want to do it

01:10.910 --> 01:11.868
你想拍，你拍
You want to do it

01:11.893 --> 01:13.348
这就是导演
He is the director

01:13.373 --> 01:15.065
导演师傅 您好 您好
Sir! Hello, sir! Nice to meet you

01:16.959 --> 01:19.436
您抽烟 我刚那买的宇宙牌香烟
Have a cigarette. I just bought this pack

01:20.686 --> 01:22.151
我不收
I can't accept that

01:22.176 --> 01:23.301
我不收
No, I really can't

01:24.119 --> 01:24.896
那我就先收着了
Then I'll keep it myself

01:27.862 --> 01:29.862
让他试试
Give him a chance

01:30.066 --> 01:32.161
让我试试啦
Just let me give it a try

01:32.363 --> 01:32.858
那太好了
Wonderful

01:34.097 --> 01:35.540
下面请看小品
And now, please enjoy the sketch

01:36.360 --> 01:37.400
吃面
"Eat Noodles"

01:38.908 --> 01:40.228
你演过电影吗
Have you ever acted in a movie

01:40.256 --> 01:42.840
我，啊...那个《少林寺红牡丹》
Well, there's The Red Peony of Shaolin Temple...（Note: A made-up Kung Fu title）

01:43.140 --> 01:44.600
《火烧圆明园》 《南征北战》
The Burning of the Imperial Palace, From Victory to Victory...(Note: A massive historical epic)

01:44.740 --> 01:45.280
《风雨下钟山》
Storm over Zhongshan...(Note: Serious war classics)

01:45.660 --> 01:46.180
不不不
No, no, no

01:46.825 --> 01:48.400
我问你演过什么角色吗
I mean, have you ever acted in one

01:49.590 --> 01:50.620
角色
Acted?

01:50.979 --> 01:51.776
没演过
No

01:52.162 --> 01:53.382
我都看过
But I've seen them all

01:54.098 --> 01:54.858
都看过
Every single one

01:55.040 --> 01:56.040
我是电影就看
If it's a movie, I would watch it

01:56.180 --> 01:56.900
我是个电影迷
I am a fan of movies

01:56.900 --> 01:57.160
导演
Sir

01:57.580 --> 01:58.134
导演
Sir

01:58.766 --> 02:02.375
你一定得答应我这个电影热爱者的这么一点起码的要求
You have to grant one small request from a movie lover

02:02.740 --> 02:03.480
让我也出出名
Let me be famous too

02:04.550 --> 02:05.255
什么
What

02:05.868 --> 02:06.708
出名
Become famous

02:08.447 --> 02:10.840
我们电影工作是革命工作的一个组成部分
Our film work is an integral part of the revolutionary cause

02:11.136 --> 02:12.216
是为人民服务的
In service of the people

02:12.300 --> 02:13.760
你怎么那是出名的机会呢
How can you think it's about becoming famous

02:13.800 --> 02:14.155
对对对
correct, correct

02:14.180 --> 02:16.280
我刚才是说走口了
It was a slip of the tongue

02:16.829 --> 02:18.092
我就是这个意思
This is exactly what I mean

02:18.300 --> 02:19.520
让给 给我呢
Please let me..

02:20.857 --> 02:23.720
也有这么一个为革命工作的机会
a chance to contribute as well

02:26.460 --> 02:27.820
好
Alright

02:27.820 --> 02:28.660
就是吃面
All you'll do is eat noodles

02:28.960 --> 02:29.620
吃面
Eat noodles?

02:29.760 --> 02:30.020
你看
Look

02:31.060 --> 02:31.900
这是一碗面
Here's a bowl of noodles

02:32.784 --> 02:33.800
我今天正好没吃饭
What perfect timing, I'm actually starving

02:34.180 --> 02:35.629
你说什么
What did you say

02:36.282 --> 02:38.080
我说我今天一定好好干
I said I'll do my best

02:38.440 --> 02:39.620
来来来
Come come

02:40.040 --> 02:40.900
一定好好干
I'll do my very best

02:41.738 --> 02:43.120
好了我们各部门都注意了
Alright, everyone, pay attention

02:43.864 --> 02:45.680
化妆服妆道具都准备
Makeup, costumes, props, get ready.

02:45.880 --> 02:46.953
打卤面
Noodles with Meat Gravy

02:47.040 --> 02:48.040
摄影机的位置
Camera position

02:48.792 --> 02:50.200
咱们可以再稍微暗一点
Let's make it a little darker

02:50.620 --> 02:50.820
稍微记一下
Note a bit

02:51.660 --> 02:52.040
好
Good

02:52.040 --> 02:52.582
好嘞
Alright

02:53.146 --> 02:54.744
什么声音
What's that Sound

02:57.658 --> 02:58.522
安静
Quiet on set

02:58.720 --> 03:00.060
诶 照明组
Hey, lighting group

03:00.320 --> 03:02.240
咱们这个演员的表演器在这儿
Our actor’s marks are right here

03:02.280 --> 03:02.880
光 光这儿呢
Keep the lights right here

03:03.000 --> 03:03.520
好嘞 好嘞
Got it, got it

03:03.560 --> 03:03.720
好好
Good, good

03:04.460 --> 03:05.990
什么声
What is that sound

03:07.151 --> 03:08.011
安静
Silence

03:11.599 --> 03:12.760
别笑
Stop laughing

03:14.340 --> 03:15.500
咱们各部分都加紧准备啊
Everyone, speed up the preparations

03:16.732 --> 03:18.280
这一段演员的戏是
Now, the actor’s scene for this part is...

03:26.297 --> 03:28.029
你怎么给吃上了
Why are you already eating it?!

03:28.620 --> 03:30.840
不瞒您说 我今早饭就没吃
To be honest with you, I didn't even have breakfast today

03:30.940 --> 03:32.100
我先垫个底儿
I'm just putting a baseline down

03:32.800 --> 03:34.740
这还没开拍呢
We haven't even started filming yet!

03:35.258 --> 03:37.524
没关系 我看那儿还一捅呢
It's fine. I see you’ve got a whole bucket over there anyway

03:38.900 --> 03:40.300
这段戏是这个样子的
The scene goes like this:

03:40.600 --> 03:42.740
你和你的女朋友已经约好了
You and your girlfriend have a date

03:42.900 --> 03:44.300
今晚八点钟一起看电影
To see a movie together at 8:00 PM tonight

03:44.800 --> 03:45.540
哦 恋爱戏
Oh, a romance scene

03:47.300 --> 03:48.700
现在是
And now it is...

03:48.760 --> 03:51.660
导演 我从小就喜欢看恋爱的电影
Sir, I've loved watching romance movies since I was a kid

03:51.940 --> 03:53.280
你别啰嗦
Stop babbling

03:54.007 --> 03:55.234
现在已经八点钟了
It is already 8:00 PM

03:55.268 --> 03:55.677
八点了
8:00 PM

03:55.800 --> 03:56.460
你正在吃面
You are in the middle of eating your noodles

03:56.557 --> 03:57.680
你的女朋友来叫你
Your girlfriend comes to call for you

03:57.820 --> 03:59.240
你吃完了面放下完就跑出
You finish your noodles, put down the bowl, and run out...

03:59.300 --> 04:00.060
放下碗就跑出
Put down and run out...

04:00.060 --> 04:00.800
就这点词啊
Are these the only lines

04:00.800 --> 04:00.940
哎
Yeah

04:01.300 --> 04:02.240
一共两句词
Just two lines in total

04:02.420 --> 04:02.900
两句词
Two lines

04:03.160 --> 04:03.415
哎
Yeah

04:03.440 --> 04:04.380
你着什么急吗
What's your rush

04:04.420 --> 04:04.920
我不着急
I'm not rushing

04:07.079 --> 04:08.600
我说一共两句台词
I said, there are only two lines in total

04:08.940 --> 04:09.720
你着什么急
What's your rush

04:09.740 --> 04:11.120
是，一共两句台词
Yes, just two lines

04:11.340 --> 04:11.880
我不着急
I am not rushing

04:12.280 --> 04:13.180
不是
No, that's not it...

04:13.548 --> 04:15.960
我说的是一共两句台词
What I am saying is, "There are only two lines in total!"

04:16.079 --> 04:16.280
对啊
Right

04:16.359 --> 04:17.239
你着什么急
What's your rush?

04:17.420 --> 04:18.180
我真的不着急
I really am not rushing

04:18.340 --> 04:18.519
导演
Sir

04:19.672 --> 04:21.439
我说一共两句台词
I'm telling you: "There are only two lines in total!"

04:21.500 --> 04:22.245
你着什么...
What's your...

04:22.314 --> 04:24.452
两句台词我着什么急
I know just two lines, so why the hell should I rush?!

04:24.980 --> 04:25.780
好了
Alright, alright!

04:25.780 --> 04:26.320
你别说话！
Shut up and stop talking!

04:26.460 --> 04:26.840
哎 是
Uh, yes sir

04:28.700 --> 04:29.540
你别说
Don't say a word

04:29.760 --> 04:30.578
我不说
I won't

04:31.119 --> 04:32.279
一共两句台词
There are only two lines in total...

04:32.619 --> 04:33.559
是你说的
...is what YOU are supposed to say!

04:35.757 --> 04:36.913
你着什么急嘛
"What's your rush?"

04:37.400 --> 04:38.640
你等我一会儿嘛
"Just wait for me for a bit."

04:38.900 --> 04:40.960
哦 我好像明白了
Oh I think I get it now

04:41.250 --> 04:41.560
啊
Ah

04:41.940 --> 04:43.200
是我说的
Those are my lines!

04:43.340 --> 04:43.720
你说的
Your lines

04:44.099 --> 04:45.601
你说一遍, 我听听
Try them once, let me hear it.

04:46.449 --> 04:46.987
啊
Ah

04:47.060 --> 04:47.440
说一遍
Say them once?

04:47.860 --> 04:48.620
啊
Ah

04:49.560 --> 04:50.400
就这么说
Just deliver them like that

04:50.743 --> 04:52.160
当然就带情绪了
With the feeling, of course

04:52.160 --> 04:53.320
哦 带点情绪
Ah, with a bit of feeling

04:54.340 --> 04:56.489
哎 你着什么急 等我一会儿
"Hey, what's your rush? Wait for me for a bit!"

04:57.083 --> 04:58.689
这个意思
Which means...

04:58.926 --> 05:00.676
你已经晚了
You are already late

05:00.700 --> 05:02.580
要表现出来那种歉意感
You need to show a sense of apologetic regret

05:02.798 --> 05:03.518
歉意感
A sense of apologetic

05:03.699 --> 05:04.382
对
Exactly

05:04.825 --> 05:06.269
歉意感
apologetic...

05:06.677 --> 05:08.077
哎，着什么急
"What's your rush?"

05:08.140 --> 05:09.479
等我一会儿
"Wait a bit"

05:11.905 --> 05:13.436
哎 你要边吃边说
You have to say it while eating

05:13.460 --> 05:15.560
你要边吃边说
You must say it while eating

05:15.692 --> 05:16.441
这种意思
Like this vibe

05:16.580 --> 05:18.240
你着什么急
"What's your rush?"

05:20.734 --> 05:22.271
你真的盛碗面
You should actually dish up a real bowl of noodles

05:22.509 --> 05:23.876
找点吃面的感觉
Get into the zone of actually eating noodles

05:24.112 --> 05:24.472
真的？
For real?

05:26.415 --> 05:28.213
还要我吃一碗啊
I get another bowl?!

05:34.938 --> 05:35.777
哎，哎，盛满
Okay，Fill it up

05:36.199 --> 05:37.360
我们各部门都注意了
Attention, all departments!

05:37.500 --> 05:38.451
看一下演员的戏
Prepare for the actor's performance rehearsal

05:38.626 --> 05:39.436
马上就开拍
We will roll immediately.

05:43.699 --> 05:44.860
好
Good

05:45.280 --> 05:46.400
来
Alright, lets go

05:46.920 --> 05:47.919
预备
ready

05:48.575 --> 05:49.948
您先吃
You eat first, please

05:52.483 --> 05:54.023
那我就不客气
Okay, don't mind if I start

05:54.860 --> 05:56.100
来 开始
And... Action!

05:58.490 --> 06:00.210
说 着什么急
Say it! "What's your rush"

06:01.171 --> 06:02.131
吃的要猛啊
Eat like you're starving

06:02.160 --> 06:03.105
要猛 要猛
starving, starving

06:03.240 --> 06:03.839
行
Okay!

06:04.074 --> 06:05.121
没问题
No problem!

06:06.828 --> 06:07.536
说 你着什么急
Say it! "What's your rush?"

06:07.561 --> 06:08.941
说 你着什么急
Say it! "What's your rush?"

06:09.340 --> 06:11.320
台词 说你着什么急
Your line! Say, "What's your rush?"

06:11.495 --> 06:12.015
等一会儿
"Hold on a second!"

06:12.040 --> 06:13.128
吃 要猛
Eat! Fiercely

06:13.622 --> 06:14.775
越猛能够表达人性的
The more fiercely you eat, the more it reflects human nature...

06:14.800 --> 06:15.800
越能够
The more it can...

06:15.820 --> 06:17.220
越能够表达出现
The more it can manifest...

06:17.480 --> 06:18.380
一会儿把我把你当过来
In a moment, I will bring you—you bring yourself over here...

06:18.560 --> 06:19.080
你当过来
You come over here

06:19.200 --> 06:19.400
你当过来
You come over here

06:19.640 --> 06:21.080
好 把我把你当过来
Good, I'll bring you—you bring yourself over

06:21.104 --> 06:22.803
放 把它放下
Put it... put it down

06:22.920 --> 06:23.583
放一下 放一下
Put it down! Put it down!

06:23.777 --> 06:24.327
跑出去
Run away!

06:24.733 --> 06:26.600
跑跑跑
And run, run, run!

06:26.704 --> 06:27.564
跑
run!

06:27.760 --> 06:28.500
回来
Come back!

06:34.080 --> 06:34.700
你感觉怎么样
How do you feel?

06:35.120 --> 06:36.240
味道不错
Delicious

06:38.276 --> 06:39.676
什么味道不错
What do you mean, "Delicious"?

06:39.700 --> 06:41.560
面条 咸淡正好
The noodles. The saltiness is just right

06:41.920 --> 06:43.960
我没问你这个
I didn't ask you about that!

06:44.140 --> 06:45.792
我问你这个
I am asking you about this..

06:46.380 --> 06:47.140
感觉怎么样
...how do you feel?

06:47.921 --> 06:49.321
饱了
Full

06:49.675 --> 06:50.893
这全拧了
It's all totally messed up!

06:50.981 --> 06:52.149
不拧
Not at all

06:52.946 --> 06:55.528
我问你刚才这段戏的感觉怎么样
I am asking how you felt about your acting

06:56.708 --> 06:57.285
戏的感觉
The acting?

06:57.394 --> 07:00.469
戏...没什么感觉
The acting... didn't feel much of anything about the acting

07:02.380 --> 07:03.786
这怎么都没感觉呢 这个戏
How can you have no feeling at all for this scene

07:03.861 --> 07:05.781
我就感觉味还不错
I just felt the flavor was quite nice

07:06.397 --> 07:07.046
别的没有
Nothing else

07:07.180 --> 07:07.910
好了
Alright

07:08.175 --> 07:09.953
对你要求也不能太高感觉
I shouldn't expect more from you

07:10.060 --> 07:10.860
不不不 导演
No, no, no, Sir

07:11.520 --> 07:12.200
咱们这么说吧
Let's put it this way:

07:12.318 --> 07:13.658
您一定得严格要求我
You absolutely must hold me to the strictest standards

07:15.170 --> 07:16.967
这个您看着我哪不合适
Wherever you think I'm not behaviour...

07:17.320 --> 07:18.600
您批评我
...you criticize me!

07:19.040 --> 07:19.440
您骂我
scold me!

07:19.620 --> 07:21.040
您打我都行
Even beat me! Anything is fine

07:21.040 --> 07:22.620
只要能出名
As long as I can get famous...

07:23.052 --> 07:24.322
我又说走口了
Whoops, slip of the tongue again

07:24.424 --> 07:26.836
只要咱们都是为工作嘛, 是不是
As long as we're both doing it for the work, right?

07:27.097 --> 07:27.859
好了好了
Fine, fine

07:28.340 --> 07:28.560
来吧
Lets try again

07:29.160 --> 07:29.700
你盛面吧
Dish up the noodles

07:29.940 --> 07:30.245
盛面
Dish 'em up

07:30.360 --> 07:30.620
盛面
Dish 'em up

07:32.580 --> 07:33.420
盛面盛面
Dishing up, dishing up!

07:33.840 --> 07:35.000
就这一碗了吧
This is the final bowl, right?

07:35.391 --> 07:36.151
真是你开始盛面
Dish 'em up!

07:36.316 --> 07:36.696
太好了
okay

